TITLE: Defining a Basic Remote Element in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates a simple custom element by extending the RemoteElement base class and registering it with the customElements registry.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
import {RemoteElement} from '@remote-dom/core/elements';

class MyElement extends RemoteElement {}

customElements.define('my-element', MyElement);
```

