TITLE: Defining RemoteFragmentElement as a Generic Container in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to define a RemoteFragmentElement, which is used as a generic container for certain APIs in @remote-dom/preact and @remote-dom/react. It demonstrates how to import and define the custom element.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import {RemoteFragmentElement} from '@remote-dom/core/elements';

customElements.define('remote-fragment', RemoteFragmentElement);
```

