TITLE: Manually Synchronizing Remote Attributes
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to manually observe and synchronize attributes between remote and host environments by implementing the attributeChangedCallback method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
import {RemoteElement} from '@remote-dom/core/elements';

class MyElement extends RemoteElement {
  static get observedAttributes() {
    return ['label'];
  }

  attributeChangedCallback(name, oldValue, newValue) {
    if (name === 'label') {
      this.updateRemoteAttribute('label', newValue);
    }
  }
}

customElements.define('my-element', MyElement);
```

