TITLE: Adding Event Listeners to Remote Elements
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add event listeners to a remote element that will respond to events dispatched by the host environment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const element = document.createElement('my-element');
element.addEventListener('change', () => console.log('Changed!'));
```

