TITLE: Simplified Remote Properties Definition
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to define remote properties using the static remoteProperties getter for automatic attribute/property handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import {RemoteElement} from '@remote-dom/core/elements';

class MyElement extends RemoteElement {
  static get remoteProperties() {
    return ['label'];
  }
}

customElements.define('my-element', MyElement);
```

