TITLE: Setting Attributes on Remote Elements
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a remote element instance and set an attribute that will be synchronized with the host environment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const element = document.createElement('my-element');
element.setAttribute('label', 'Hello, world!');
```

