TITLE: Basic Remote Property Implementation in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to manually implement a remote property using updateRemoteProperty() method in a RemoteElement subclass.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/remote-dom/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import {RemoteElement} from '@remote-dom/core/elements';

class MyElement extends RemoteElement {
  #label;

  get label() {
    return this.#label;
  }

  set label(value) {
    this.#label = value;
    this.updateRemoteProperty('label', value);
  }
}

customElements.define('my-element', MyElement);
```

